        "title": "The <i>Plasmodium falciparum</i> rhoptry protein RhopH3 plays essential roles in host cell invasion and nutrient uptake", 
        "published": "2017-03-02T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2017-03-02T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 6, 
